unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(idActorDamager, idActorDamaged)

--Disabling gizmo so you can't click on it
Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(gizmo_DemonBubble, true)

--After you hit pillar once, this makes it invulnerable and untargetable 
Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(monster_Pillar, true)
Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(monster_Pillar, false)

--Enable the gizmo visually
Hydra.ActorEnable(gizmo_DemonBubble)

--Wave event
for i, Spawner in ipairs(tWave01Spawners) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(Spawner)
	end
	
end

unk_98d4504.value:
-- Re-getting actors in this group in case any have turned off after 
-- spawning their max lifetime monsters. Otherwise we get a nil error.

tWave01Spawners = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_VGN_TriuneRitual_01")
for i, Spawner in ipairs(tWave01Spawners) do
	Hydra.ActorDisable(Spawner)
end

Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()
